DESCRIPTION:What happens when art meets memes? Come find out by turning artworks featuring cats into your own witty meme in this edition of Make at MAP.\n\nMake @ MAP is a series that allows you to explore our collection in an engaging and hands-on manner. These sessions allow you to create and take home a special souvenir of your visit. It is perfect for all ages — so bring your friends and family and get ready to make some art! No experience is necessary\, just a willingness to have fun and experiment with new materials.
DTEND:20260329T093000Z
DTSTART:20260329T053000Z
SUMMARY:Make at MAP
